A delivery for Midwife Catherine. It's completely unclear how this

Officially called a medical coupon. It permits the business of
prostitutes and guarantees their health status.
name: Yellow Identification Tag

description:
A goblin child entrusted by the adventurer Sharly. It wriggles eerily
in one's arms.
name: Shirley's Child

description: Milk squeezed from Serena's own breasts.
name: Serena's Milk

name: Milk

description:
An apparatus for pregnant women to manually express excess breast
milk. It somewhat relieves the tension in the breasts.
name: Milking Machine

description:
A goblin baby born from Serena. Lacking any of the usual cuteness of
infants, it's an ugly creature.
name: Goblin Child

description:
An orc baby born from Serena. Its bony and muscular body is already
too heavy to hold.
name: Orc Child

description:
A warg baby born from Serena. It grows quickly and seems like it would
walk endlessly if put on the floor.
name: Warg Child

description:
A pigman baby born from Serena. Its squishy skin induces a
physiological disgust in the mother.
name: Pigman Child

description:
A stallion baby born from Serena. Violent is an understatement;
feeding it feels more like plunder than nursing.
name: Stallion Child

description:
A slime spawn that came out of Serena's body. Communication is
difficult, and it's hard to tell if it's even asleep.
name: Slime Larva

description:
A roper baby born from Serena. Occasionally, it seems to try to
entangle and capture its surroundings.
name: Roper Child

description: A chimera baby born from Serena.
name: Chimera Child

description:
A baby of unknown fatherhood born from Serena. Innocently sleeping for
now...
name: Someone's Child

description:
A baby made with John that Serena carries. Each time she holds it
close, dreadful memories flash through her mind.
name: Random Attacker John's Child

description:
The child Serena made with Gie. The smell of the prison comes back to
me.
name: Child of Guy

description:
The child Serena made with the innkeeper Vincent. I have no memory of
it, and it terrifies me.
name: Child of Vincent

description: The child Serena made with Albert. The child is quiet while nursing.
name: Child of Albert

description: The child Serena made with Samuel. The child is quiet while nursing.
name: Child of Samuel

description:
The child Serena made with the weapon shop owner Doni. I don't feel at
all like a parent, nor that this child is mine.
name: Child of Denis

description: The child Serena made with Mathias. The child is quiet while nursing.
name: Child of Mathias

description: The child Serena made with Marcel. The child is quiet while nursing.
name: Child of Marcel

description:
The child Serena made with the brothel's foreman Deacon. Deacon's
overly familiar behavior makes me feel sick.
name: Child of Deacon

description: The child Serena made with the city noble Goupil.
name: Child of Goobil

description:
The child Serena made with the captain of the city guard Demouran. I
just can't find it in me to think of the child as cute.
name: Child of Demulan

description:
The child Serena made with the town doctor Rodrigue. I hope at least
this child grows up properly.
name: Child of Rodrigue

description:
The child Serena made with Gekuran. When I try to think about this
child, my mind gets foggy.
name: Child of Geklan

description: The child Serena made with Tim.
name: Child of Tim

description:
The child Serena made with Ganelon. A symbol of humiliation, violence,
and submission. I just can't bring myself to love it.
name: Child of Ganelon

description:
The child Serena made with Bardan. Although the child was not wanted,
I wish for its happiness.
name: Child of Bardan

description:
The child Serena made with someone from the city guard. Since the
guards cowardly hide their faces, the parent of this child is unknown.
name: Child of a City Guard Member

description:
The child Serena made with a guild member. No, they're not my
comrades. Not those who would do such a thing.
name: Child of an Adventurer

description:
The child Serena made with a thug. I was raped and forcibly
impregnated. It's impossible to harbor any affection.
name: Child of a Thug

description:
The child Serena made with a punk. The men's vulgar laughter still
clings to my ears and won't leave.
name: Child of a Punk

description:
The child Serena made with a vagrant. The child's responses are slow,
and its eyes are vacant. It's unsettling to watch.
name: Child of a Vagrant

description:
The child Serena made with a prostitution client. I don't know his
name. It makes me feel very miserable.
name: Child of a Prostitute's Client

description:
Serena's child, born amidst the prisoners. Days like hell. And its
continuation still lies in my hands.
name: Prisoner's Child

description:
Serena's child, sired by a stud stallion. I've given birth. That man
must be sneering.
name: Stallion's Child

description:
Serena's child, fathered by Ganelon's son. Will this child grow up to
hurt and violate someone, just like me?
name: Ganelon's Grandchild

description:
Serena's child, conceived with a goblin of her own blood. A squared
abomination. An existence that should never be forgiven.
name: Goblin's Offspring

description:
Serena's child, conceived with an orc of her own blood. It must be
disposed of quickly. It must be disposed of soon...
name: Orc's Offspring

description:
Serena's child, conceived with a warg of her own blood. My hands
tremble as I hold it. I want to throw it away right now.
name: Warg's Offspring

description:
Serena's child, conceived with a pigman of her own blood. Could there
be any other sin as terrifying as this in the world?
name: Pigman's Offspring

description:
Serena's child, conceived with a stallion of her own blood. A huge
penis stands erect. Pure terror.
name: Stallion's Offspring

description:
Serena's child, conceived with a roper of her own blood. I've already
been attacked by it several times. If this continues...
name: Roper's Offspring
